summary: I decided to share my preset of one of my new characters. Make any adjustments you like or don't :D
descriptionHtml:
It can be annoying making a new character if I do say so myself. For male characters it's rather easy but for female characters it tends to be hard to get it right. So i've provided a preset for everyone if you wish to skip creating a new character from scratch:

You at least need:
ECE
SG Hair Pack (Hellosanta)

Char Mods I use:
SG Hair Pack
ECE
Fair Skin Complexion UNP (Works for 7base as well)
UNP
author: ArcticKoalaMoose
